Bootstrap: docker
From: python:3.11-slim

%post
    pip install --no-cache-dir numpy scipy pandas matplotlib

%environment
    export LC_ALL=C
    export PATH=/usr/local/bin:$PATH

%runscript
    python3 "$@"

%labels
    Author GuillaumeJmt
    Version 1.0
    Description Scientific Python container for HPC

%help
    Scientific Python container: numpy, scipy, pandas, matplotlib.
    MPI is intentionally not bundled: installing mpi4py inside a slim image fails
    (no MPI library/compiler), and the correct HPC pattern is to bind-mount the
    host MPI (hybrid model) for interconnect ABI compatibility.
